Secure Copy

Copy file from a remote host to local host:
scp username@target:someFile localLocation

Copy file from local host to a remote host:
scp someFile username@target:someLocation

Copy file from remote how to another remote host:
scp usernam@targetA:someFile username@targetB:someFile

You can pass -r to recursively copy folders and files
You can pass -C to enable compression
You can pass -P to specify a port to connect to on the remote host

